&lt;li&gt;Experience managing longer, complex sales cycles. This includes navigating the complexity of multiple buying stakeholders and the nuances of government buying&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating with an internal channel partner team to sell through and with channel partners is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant software or hardware industry experience in any of the following domains; security software or hardware, computer networking and ‚Äúhow the internet works‚Äù, subscription, SaaS, or Cloud software is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
